column5: just wondering if anyone here wants to hook up during the day tomorow for some pike around scarborough, know of a couple of spots that produced last week.  pm me or add me on msn [emailÂ protected]  btw* anyone here about a body being found at the ganny today???
I'm available around 12:30-1ish? if you plan to go then, I can linkup with you then!
I am going to be cruising around Scarborough and Pickering today with my pike tackle.  I will probably see you guys around!

Was up at the Ganny this morning for a look.....Police have the little park at the end taped off with police tape, and an officer on guard. Didnt know what was up but read about it in the Toronto Star when I got back.   Expected to see more people fishing.....first time there for me, but did not fish. Just went to have a look because I was thinking of going tomorrow....
Hey l2p, nice hookin' up with you today bud. Hopefully next time around we'll get a bit more lucky... and actually hook one!
sluggish day = sluggish fish. next time for sure!
